node.text: There’s a beautiful campaign going on right now @printsforwildlife to raise critically needed funding for conservation through a unique 30-day print sale of some of the best wildlife photography out there. Over 170 globally renowned wildlife photographers from National Geographic, Sony, Nikon and Canon Ambassadors among others are donating an iconic image – where only 100 copies of each photo are available - for just $100. 100% of proceeds after printing and handling is going to @AfricanParksNetwork – a conservation organization that manages 19 parks in 11 countries across Africa for wildlife and people. They’ve already raised $500K in the first two weeks, and have a goal of hitting $1M. Visit Gallery: https://bit.ly/3wxfnmV
